LINK - https://in.indeed.com/q-sound-engineer-jobs.html?vjk=48090529ecf1c6b3
Full job description
Job Title: Audio Editor

Company: Vrinda Media Lab

Location: Faridabad, Haryana.

Job Type: Full-time

Experience: 1-2 years

About Vrinda Media Lab:

Vrinda Media Lab is an innovative and forward-thinking media production company specializing in Video Editing, Audio Editing and Sound Design. As a company committed to excellence in audiovisual storytelling, we are seeking a talented Audio Editor to join our creative team.

Job Overview:

We are looking for a skilled and creative Audio Editor with 1-2 years of experience to contribute to the success of our projects at Vrinda Media Lab. The ideal candidate will be proficient in using industry-standard audio editing software, with a primary focus on Pro Tools. In addition to technical proficiency, strong communication skills are essential for effective collaboration with the creative team.

Responsibilities:

Edit and synchronize audio elements to enhance the overall quality of the final product.
Use Pro Tools and other relevant software to manipulate and improve audio quality.
Ensure audio content meets industry standards and project specifications.
Work closely with video editors, sound designers, and other team members to achieve a cohesive audiovisual experience.
Stay updated on industry trends and advancements in audio editing.
Requirements:

Bachelor's degree.
Proven experience as an Audio Editor with a portfolio showcasing previous work.
Proficiency in Pro Tools and other industry-standard audio editing software.
Must be Proficient in English.
Ability to work within tight deadlines without compromising quality.

